General.Name: United Maritime Corporation
General.Description: United Maritime Corporation, a shipping company, offers seaborne transportation services worldwide. The company operates a fleet of eight dry bulk vessels comprising three Panamax, three Capesize, and two Kamsarmax vessels with an aggregate cargo-carrying capacity of approximately 922,072 dwt. United Maritime Corporation was incorporated in 2022 and is based in Glyfada, Greece.
